name: DOGFART
description: DOGFART is a meme + deflationary ecosystem token on X Layer. It pairs with $DOGSHIT and NFTs to form a dual-mechanism system: • $DOGFART continuously deflates through burns. • $DOGSHIT gains empowerment and utility via the burn mechanism. • NFT integration amplifies community participation with additional rewards. Together, they create a sustainable ecosystem that supports community-driven building and long-term growth on X Layer.
